  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large paella pan or skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chicken broth, saffron threads, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the masarepa to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for 5-7 minutes or until the masarepa is cooked through and the mixture is creamy.",
    "Remove from heat and let rest for 5 minutes before serving."
